        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "The art of making chocolate from scratch transforms raw cacao beans into the richest, most rewarding treat you will ever taste.",
            "fg": "#F5E6D3",
            "bg": "#1C0F05"
          },
          {
            "type": "box",
            "width": "100%",
            "height": 9,
            "backgroundColor": "#2A1A0A",
            "border": true,
            "borderStyle": "solid",
            "borderColor": "#D4A574",
            "title": "Ingredients",
            "titleAlignment": "left",
            "padding": 1,
            "gap": 0,
            "flexDirection": "column",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Cacao beans ............ 200 g  (raw, whole, fermented)",
                "fg": "#E8C9A0",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Cacao butter ........... 50 g   (for smoother texture)",
                "fg": "#E8C9A0",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Sugar .................. 80 g   (powdered, adjust to taste)",
                "fg": "#E8C9A0",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Pinch of salt .......... enhances depth and flavour",
                "fg": "#E8C9A0",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "box",
            "width": "100%",
            "height": 16,
            "backgroundColor": "#2A1A0A",
            "border": true,
            "borderStyle": "solid",
            "borderColor": "#D4A574",
            "title": "Step-by-Step Process",
            "titleAlignment": "left",
            "padding": 1,
            "gap": 0,
            "flexDirection": "column",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  1) ROAST  Spread beans on a tray. Roast at 150 C for 20-25 min.",
                "fg": "#F5E6D3",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "              You will hear cracking. The aroma deepens to rich cocoa.",
                "fg": "#A07850",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  2) WINNOW  Cool beans, then crush and blow off the husks.",
                "fg": "#F5E6D3",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "              You want only the dark nibs inside. Discard the shells.",
                "fg": "#A07850",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  3) GRIND  Blend nibs in a high-power grinder for 15-30 min.",
                "fg": "#F5E6D3",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "              Nibs melt into a thick, aromatic paste called cocoa liquor.",
                "fg": "#A07850",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  4) CONCH  Continue grinding 1-4 hours for silky smoothness.",
                "fg": "#F5E6D3",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "              Add cacao butter and sugar gradually during this stage.",
                "fg": "#A07850",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  5) TEMPER  Heat to 50 C, cool to 28 C, reheat to 31-32 C.",
                "fg": "#F5E6D3",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "              Proper temper gives the snap, shine, and stable crystals.",
                "fg": "#A07850",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  6) MOLD & SET  Pour into molds, tap to release air bubbles,",
                "fg": "#F5E6D3",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "              refrigerate 30 min. Pop out and enjoy your creation!",
                "fg": "#A07850",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "box",
            "width": "100%",
            "height": 9,
            "backgroundColor": "#2A1A0A",
            "border": true,
            "borderStyle": "solid",
            "borderColor": "#D4A574",
            "title": "Pro Tips",
            "titleAlignment": "left",
            "padding": 1,
            "gap": 0,
            "flexDirection": "column",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Roast lighter for fruity notes; darker for deep, earthy flavour.",
                "fg": "#FFD700",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Use a melangeur or wet grinder for the smoothest conching results.",
                "fg": "#FFD700",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Never let water touch your chocolate; even a drop causes seizing.",
                "fg": "#FFD700",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "content": "  Add vanilla, cinnamon, or chili during conching for artisan bars.",
                "fg": "#FFD700",
                "bg": "#2A1A0A"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "box",
            "width": "100%",
            "height": 7,
            "backgroundColor": "#2A1A0A",
